<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#49914782a5127e78dfa8d9cb36377bbb>.
<#49914782a5127e78dfa8d9cb36377bbb> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/U26493>;
